<p><strong>TU Berlin Summer University</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The TU Berlin Summer and Winter University is looking forward to launchi=
ng its first 2017 winter program, welcoming international students to the G=
erman capital for four weeks of academic study at the Berlin Institute of T=
echnology (TU Berlin).</p>
<p>The following courses will start from January 3rd 2017:</p>
<p><a href=3D"http://www.tu-berlin.de/menue/summer_university/winter_univer=
sity/cansat_hands_on_satellite_design/">CanSat: Hands-on Satellite Design</=
a>
<br>
A CanSat is a small satellite in shape of a commercial beverage can that pe=
rforms several measuring tasks. In this course, a CanSat is designed, built=
 and tested in the field during a rocket launch.</p>
<p><a href=3D"http://www.tu-berlin.de/menue/summer_university/winter_univer=
sity/programming_in_java/">Programming in Java</a>
<br>
In this course students will learn how to write computer programs in the pr=
ogramming language Java. Students will work individually and in groups, wit=
h the course culminating in a big project at the end.</p>
<p><a href=3D"http://www.tu-berlin.de/menue/summer_university/winter_univer=
sity/startup_crash_course_from_idea_to_reality">Startup Crash Course: From =
Idea to Reality</a>
<br>
This course is for budding entrepreneurs who want to gain insight into laun=
ching a startup. Participants will learn theory, have guest talks from star=
tup owners in Berlin, and will work on their own business models in groups,=
 which they will pitch to investors
 in a mock investor pitch.</p>
<p>TU Berlin will also be running the third 2017 summer program, from June =
to August, with many wide range of courses. Please click
<a href=3D"http://www.tu-berlin.de/menue/summer_university/summer_universit=
y/">here</a> for more information.</p>
<p>You can also learn more about us on the <a href=3D"http://www.winter-uni=
versity.tu-berlin.de/">
website</a> and social media channels such as <a href=3D"https://www.facebo=
ok.com/TU-Berlin-Summer-University-1398999673750476/">
Facebook</a>. Find the full course list <a href=3D"http://www.tu-berlin.de/=
menue/summer_university/winter_university/">
here</a>. Registration is <a href=3D"http://www.tu-berlin.de/menue/summer_u=
niversity/register/">
online</a> now!</p>
